<includeonly><div class="gb-figure gb-figure-{{#switch:{{{align|}}}|left=left|right=right|center=center|#default=none}}" style="width:{{#if:{{{width|}}}|{{{width}}}px|auto}}" data-full="{{{full|}}}">
{{{src|}}}
{{#if:{{{caption|}}}|<div class="gb-figure-caption">{{{caption}}}</div>}}
</div>{{#if:{{{src|}}}|{{#set:Has body image={{{src}}}}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Floated, captioned body image served from the legacy Giant Bomb CDN. Emitted by the figure re-migration (docs/figure-formatting-remigration.md); the bare src URL renders as an external image via $wgAllowExternalImagesFrom. Each use also annotates [[Property:Has_body_image]] so /Images subpages can query in-use images. full= is stored as data-full for a future lightbox/click-through.

Usage:
<pre>
{{GBFigure
|src=https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/ignore_jpg_scale_medium/0/1992/1462560-map_antonica_hi.gif
|full=https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/1992/1462560-map_antonica_hi.gif
|align=left
|width=350
|caption=Map of Antonica
}}
</pre>

